Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: Are you tired of the daily grind? Do you wish you could skip ahead to a better future? Well, now you can with A Better Place Inc.!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: With our state-of-the-art cryochambers, you can take a break from the daily stress and wake up to be a better you!

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The air smells of disinfectant. I sit in the uncomfortable hospital chair outside of the Memory Hall.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: Say goodbye to the daily grind and say hello to a better life with A Better Place Inc.! Contact us today to learn more.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I close my eyes and take a deep breath.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: A robot passes by me, its screen displaying the words, "We're sorry for your loss."

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Levi, Arthur. Rose is waiting for you.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I slowly rise from the seat at the sound of my name. My mind is still heavy with grief, but I know that I need to do this.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Come on, Arthur. Don’t be a coward.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I approach the door, I can feel my heart racing and my palms getting sweaty.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The medical drones hum on the background, making the silence even more unsettling.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: We offer the latest in cryosleep technology, allowing you to pause your life and wake up to a brighter tomorrow.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: Whether you want to skip ahead a few years or several decades, we have the solution for you.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Say goodbye to the daily grind and say hello to a better life with A Better Place Inc.! Contact us today to learn more.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: We say it unison, my voice thundering in the empty corridor.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I hate this ad.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Used to give me hope, but now that Gran is dead...

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: A brighter tomorrow my ass. What a load of bullshit.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: That's the most compassion I've got all day.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I let out a bitter chuckle at the sight of it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: What a mockery.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The walls are lined with electronic photo frames with pictures of loved ones passed away.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The blinking message on the display requires me to type a name of a deceased one.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I’ve never seen her smile like this. Warm, comforting. Carefree.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Her face was always etched with worry and sadness, ever since my parents died in a shuttle crash.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Hi, Gran. Sorry I haven’t been there for you when... you know.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I reach out to touch her, but my hand goes right through the hologram, breaking the illusion.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: Please refrain from touching the hologram, as it may cause damage or distortion to the image.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Alright, I need to get out of here.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: When I approach the exit, the robotic voice comes to life again.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000025D
Properties.Text: Thank you for choosing our company for your memorial services. We are sorry for your loss.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Her hologram is a perfect replica of how she looked in life, down to the smallest detail. Except one.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I wanted to make it up for her. And now...

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I approach the towering frame at the center of the room.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This place feels like a shrine.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Rose Carter, the one and only. There was no one like her.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I press the button to summon the holo. It takes a moment, but then a soft glow fills the room.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: There really wasn't. She was the best.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: She had always been so worried about the future, about me, my job.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I didn't mean for you to go through this alone. I failed you again, haven't I.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Indeed, the distortion occurs, showing a stranger's face for a split second.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I stand there, wallowing in guilt.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This is it, the last time I get to see grandma Rose. And words elude me...

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I look at the holo one last time, taking in every wrinkle on the weathered face.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: See you, Gran.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I'm so sorry I haven't been the grandson you deserve. Someday I'll live up to your expectations, you'll see.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I'm so grateful for everything you've done for me. For raising me, believing in me when I couldn't. Thanks, Gran.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Now that I've said it, I can finally leave.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I walk out of the Memory Hall, a nurse approaches me. The color of embarrassment on her face perfectly matches her hair.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: She reminds me of Erica.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Mr. Levi? I have your grandmother’s possessions if you are willing to take them.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Yes, am. I’m willing to take them and get the hell out of here.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Her confusion is obvious now. She steps away, showing a helper-bot with a small brownish packet in its extended hands.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Could you possibly wait? This thing won’t give it away, I already called the AI specialist, but it seems they are on a break...

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I quickly examine the robot, my eyes scanning its wiry body.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Don’t bother with AI-spec. Let me just...

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I slam my fist on top of the bot, setting the head panel back in place with a soft clank.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Should be okay, try it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: After a moment’s hesitation the nurse takes the package. The bot’s grip loosens. The nurse smiles in relief as I take the packet from her.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I was.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: There is a pause in the air as if she is waiting for me to continue.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I should go.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: She nods, her eyes soft with gratitude. I turn and walk away, the weight of the packet in my hand a constant reminder of my grandmother's passing.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: There’s a small red light blinking on its metal frame, indicating that something is malfunctioning.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Could have been cute in any other situation.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Tech savvy, are you?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: That's one way to put it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: An engineer then?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Used to be.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Nurse's eyes widen in horror, but then the bot comes to motion.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I bend down and open the back panel. Then type in the master key to override bot's protection and reboot the system.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The nurse watches me cautiously.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I bet she thinks I'll break it, and she'll have to pay for it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Are you an engineer then?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This is common for PACs, and easily fixable.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: We wait in silence, awkwardly. Finally, the bot chimes to life. I can see the girl is relieved.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I take the packet out of bot's grip, and it loosens, like it should.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: There is time and place for everything.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: And now is certainly not the time to pine for a former colleague...

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: ...I had zero complete conversations with.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Get a grip, Arthur!

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: My thoughts drift away for a few long moments.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: We never got a chance to get to know each other, but I liked watching her from distance. Not in a creepy way.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Her "Hello" used to be the brightest point of any day.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: ...Wait, was it creepy?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: Mr.Levi? Are you alright? Hello-o-o!

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The nurse's voice snaps me out of it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000269
Properties.Text: I have your grandmother’s possessions if you are willing to take them.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I okay whatever the procedure is with a nod.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Well, I’m not explaining it further.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I walk down the bustling city street, the neon lights of advertisements reflect off the puddles on the pavement, casting an otherworldly glow on everything around me.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Some of the ads catch my attention — a sleek, futuristic spaceship, promoting a new colony on a distant planet, promising a better life for those brave enough to make the journey.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Or should I say, for those rich enough.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I shake my head, feeling a mix of anger and sadness well up inside me.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I can’t go on like this. I need a place to think. To figure out what’s next.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I walk by a cybercafe and glance at the neon sign that reads, "CyberZone. Get a break from reality." I keep walking.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: But then stop, contemplating the idea. Maybe it's exactly what I need right now. A break.

Properties.MenuText: I could've been one of them.
Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F

Properties.MenuText: I could've been with Erica now.
Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I was never rich, but I used to have a good job. The one that offers to join the colonization program.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I could've been one of those dreamers, drifting among the stars now, if not for the accident.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: No dream is too high, they say.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: But this one certainly is.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I was never rich, but I used to have a good job. The one that offers to join the colonization program.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: That very one that Erica joined.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: No dream is too high, they say.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Mine is among the stars. Take that, dreamers.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The air in the cybercafe is thick with the scent of coffee and artificial flavors, making my stomach churn. I approach the frontdesk.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000261
Properties.Text: Welcome to CyberZone. How can I assist you?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000261
Properties.Text: Sure thing. Scan your creds. Lui here will walk you.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The girl at the desk doesn’t even look at me like she couldn’t be bothered. She just waves me to the assistant robot nearby.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I pay for two hours in advance, and Lui comes to life, leading me to a barely lit corridor with narrow booths on both sides.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Suddenly, a commotion draws my attention. I look up to see the staff carrying away the body of a young man.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I wonder what kind of world he was lost in.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Before I can explore the thought, Lui comes to a halt near one of the doors.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Please, note that CyberZone takes no responsibility for any untimely deaths from getting lost in cyberspace.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Lui buzzes away, as I sink into the chair inside, and lay the packet next to the headset.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I click the Start button on the console.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I open it anyway. There is a pile of neatly stacked documents inside.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: He is a bag of bones clothed in rugs, pale and drained of life. An unnerving smile plays on his lips, frozen in death.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I take the headset, unable to deal with whatever Gran left me. This is all that’s left of her.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I hesitate for a moment, unsure if I am ready to open it. I feel nauseous just thinking about it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Enjoy your stay with us.

Properties.MenuText: I need a place to think.
Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
0x0100000000000261
Properties.Text: Darling, this is where people come to not think.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000261
Properties.Text: Go to a shrink or something.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Fine, a booth then.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000261
Properties.Text: More like it. Scan your creds, and Lui will walk you.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I've paid medical bills for years, I know the drill. They probably charged me extra for god knows what again.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I need to clear my head before I dive into bureaucracy.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Doesn't look like personal possessions to me.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Instead I dive into the virtual reality.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: My senses are immediately bombarded with a cacophony of new sensations.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I blink, the world around me shifts and changes, adapting to my thoughts.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This is the world like it’s supposed to be. The world I never knew.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I sit on the ground, taking in the alien sight.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: Beautiful, isn’t it?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I almost jump at the sound of a feminine voice, then groan.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I turn my head just to see a familiar face. My heart skips a beat.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: I missed you.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Yeah? What did you miss most, me fixing your coffee machine or that one time we said “Hello” to each other?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: You seem grumpy today. You did great with the coffee machine, by the way. I swear the coffee tasted better.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I almost chuckle. It’s nearly impossible to get angry at that face. So I turn away.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: No shit. My only relative just died. Sorry for feeling grumpy about it.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: I’m sorry for your loss.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: She is not lost, you pretty weirdo. She is dead.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I’m the one who’s lost. She left this... void. I can't begin to understand how to fill it...

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Oh, get out, that’s not what I meant!

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Not-Erica takes her hand off my knee.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: You know, this was supposed to be my alone time. I have things... to contemplate.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: Like what?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Like what is wrong with me. Why are you here? Why not Gran? Isn’t she the one I’m dying to see one last time?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: Is she?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Yes. No... I don’t know! You tell me! Aren’t you the all-knowing AI?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: No, I’m just a pretty girl you desperately want to talk to.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I hear a smile in her voice, and it’s too much. I disconnect, tearing the headset off.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I can feel the sun's warmth on my skin and the soft breeze blowing through my hair. The ground beneath me is solid and smells of grass.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Is it that kind of cybercafe?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I know the AI is supposed to extract your deepest desires from your brain, but it needn’t rub them in.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: You can't seem to leave my thoughts today.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I've been thinking of you in the most inappropriate of places.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: She doesn't seem swayed. Definitely a projection.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: How inappropriate are we talking?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Psychopath inappropriate. Like my grandmother's memorial, for one.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I almost feel guilty. It's not the poor projection's fault that I, apparently, want her here.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000177
Properties.Text: I see. I'm sorry for your loss.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I stumble out of the cybercafe, my heart pounding. The cool air outside hits my face, but it does little to calm me down.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: My head is still spinning after the virtual reality, and I am even more confused now than I was before.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I have nowhere to go in this city. No place to stay, no friends, no job.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The city seems to stretch out forever, a maze of towering buildings. I am overwhelmed and lost in its midst, all alone.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: What has this world come to? Is there anyone left?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As if answering my question, a pile of dirty rags moves to change the sleeping position, catching my eye.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Is there any hope for this dying planet?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The dirty pile of rugs groans something through its drunken sleep.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I stop in my tracks as I suddenly see a bright spot of color amid the dullness of the city.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Will I end up like them?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: It's a flower, growing from a crack in the pavement, breaking through the asphalt.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Such a delicate thing, its vibrant petals seem to glow, bathed in the streetlights.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: A wave of shock washes over me.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I stand up, the papers fall out of the packet in my hand.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: No, it can't be.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The distinctive flower logo of A Better Place Inc. is iridescent on synthetic paper.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This city is decaying, there are very few people left. Will be even less soon.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: And then what? Work outside the dome again, fixing junk? Will it be any different?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Or I could...

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The papers in my hands feel like an easy way out. Should I take it?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: It is a gamble. What if the Earth never recovers?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: But I already feel the decision forming in my head.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: That’s what Gran always wanted for us, isn’t it? It’s her last wish, and my second chance. I don’t deserve it, but it’s there.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I let my feet carry me. Before I know it, I’m facing a tall building with the flower logo of A Better Place Inc., glowing proudly on the front.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Nowhere to go, but forward. Right, Arthur?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I bend down, the papers fall out of the packet in my hand.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I pluck the flower and tuck it away. It might've been unnecessary to kill the poor plant, but I needed this reminder of hope on me.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I catch a glimpse of the words on one of the pages, "Cryosleep Application Form" with my name written in Gran’s neat handwriting underneath.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Can it?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: All this money I’ve sent her?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I put the papers back in the packet. Very. Carefully.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Those unable to buy themselves a better future, leave for other city centers.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Start my life anew, be useful in the newborn world.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: That's not what I've dreamed of, but it's the closest thing.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: Inside, there are only two other people besides me, conversing in hushed voices, their heads bent over the brochure.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Good evening and welcome to A Better Place Inc.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: We provide various services to help humans lift burdens of their earthly existence. How may I assist you today?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Earthly existence, huh?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: May I interest you in the Dreamscape experience? We can incarnate your deepest desires for as little as 9,999 creds.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I nearly choke at the sum.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: We can replace your unreliable flesh parts with more efficient and everlasting synthetic counterparts.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: It won’t leave you even if you want it to!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Do you want to leave an imprint on the existence of your descendants? Do you wish to haunt your in-laws even after you die? We have a solution!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: We offer the latest in cryosleep technology, allowing you to pause your life and wake up to a brighter tomorrow.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Buy now to receive a 0,999% discount on the Time Traveler Plan!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Welcome to A Better Place Inc. cryosleep program, Mr. Levi. Your service plan is Optimist.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I skim through the pages and push my thumb against the bioframe on the last one.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: According to your contract, you will wake up in exactly 7305 days. Thank you for entrusting your life to A Better Place Inc.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: This is ridiculous.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I turn to the doors. Before I know it, the guard bots have me in their grip.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Dear client, by signing the contract you gave us authorization to take you to a better place forcefully in case of indecisiveness.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: The breach of contract is inadmissible.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I feel a jab of a needle in my arm and my world fades away as I slip into a deep, dreamless sleep.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Okay, Gran. Worst case scenario you'll have me over for dinner.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The smell of antiseptic hangs in the air, and heavy nausea hits me as I’m reminded of my morning outside the Memory Hall.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I hope she is in a better place Although any place is better than this bullshit.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000001400
Properties.Text: Mr. Arthur Levi. Follow me, please.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I follow a man down a sterile hallway and into a small room. In the center, there is a sleek, metallic cylinder.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: As I comply, I feel a sense of apprehension rising within me. This is it, the point of no return. My heart hammers in my chest.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000001400
Properties.Text: Change into this robe, please.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000001400
Properties.Text: It's a standard procedure, but I need you to be calm, okay? Step inside, please.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000001400
Properties.Text: I will prepare you for the procedure. There is nothing to worry about, Mr. Levi. Just relax. You’ll wake up in a better place.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I know he means well, but that sounds like a threat.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: But before I can retort, I feel a jab of a needle in my arm, and my world fades away as I slip into a deep, dreamless sleep.

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The call about Gran's passing took me by surprise. I had to urgently return to the city, and was late nonetheless.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Are you in need of bionic prosthetics? Do you lack a limb? Or even if you don’t!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Has your wife left you? Has your dog been eaten by a pack of giant rats? We have a solution! A companion for life will cost you only 99.999 creds.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: It comes with in-built military protection equipment and high-end personality integration system that makes it a perfect partner!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Meet Engram Technology, that can create your own personality construct compatible with any AI-based tech! Be eternal!

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: I put the stack of papers on the frontdesk.The robot scans the papers, and after several beeps and blinks of the panels, chimes a friendly tune.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Please, carefully read the contract and leave your bioprint on the last page. Your better life starts now!

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: We kindly remind you that your body is not guaranteed to survive the stasis. We wish you best of luck!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Wait, what? I’m not guaranteed to survive it? It didn’t say that in the contract!

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: Don't you need to like... examine me first?

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: Please, proceed to the room on your left when your name is called.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: The Optimist plan does not include a medical examination. Do you wish to buy an upgrade?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: No, I don't wish to buy anything! I need a moment to think.

Properties.Speaker: 0x0100000000000AD1
Properties.Text: According to your plan, indecision is inadmissible. Please, proceed to the room on your left when your name is called.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I can't be indecisive? What does it even mean? Is this a military camp?

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: What will you do, if I do try to leave? Report me to the governor?

Properties.Speaker: 0x01000000000017E7
Properties.Text: The cryochamber reminds me of coffins they used to put people in.

Properties.Speaker: 0x010000000000012F
Properties.Text: I've only seen one in pictures, now I get to lie in one? Lucky me... I guess.

DefaultExtendedCharacterFeature.Motivation: Заниматься такой работой, где ему больше не пришлось бы терпеть снисходительного отношения от других. Работой, которая не требует коммуникации с людьми.
DefaultExtendedCharacterFeature.InnerConflict: Он сомневается, подходящий ли он человек, чтобы обезвреживать Горацио, — так он берет на себя ответственность за жизни всех людей на корабле.
DefaultExtendedCharacterFeature.Habits: Любит задавать себе вопросы и строить гипотезы вслух, так ему проще разобраться с проблемами. Иногда подшучивает над собой.

DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Personality: Не очень хорош в общении, но умеет сильно и надолго привязываться. Готов на любые жертвы ради тех, кто ему дорог. Часто угрюм, потому что из-за характера работы приходится общаться только с недовольными людьми. Склонен к самоиронии.
DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Appearance: Темные волосы, уставшие глаза, осунувшееся лицо. Довольно высокий и хорошо сложен.

DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Personality: Непредсказуем. Забыл, как вести себя в коммуникации с людьми. Одичал за годы одиночества на корабле.
DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Appearance: Поседевшие грязные волосы, истрепавшаяся одежда, осунувшийся вид, темные мешки под глазами. Постоянно бегающие, немного безумные, глаза. Дерганая манера двигаться.

DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Personality: Дружелюбная, мотивированная, улыбчивая. Слишком увлечена своей работой, чтобы завести с кем-то по-настоящему серьезные отношения.
DefaultBasicCharacterFeature.Appearance: Молодая женщина азиатской внешности. Волосы - рыжие, вероятно, крашеные.
